# {{project_name}}

Generated with `uvx vision-agents init`.

## Setup

1. Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and fill in the keys.
2. Install dependencies:

   ```bash
   uv sync
   ```

3. Run the agent:

   ```bash
   uv run vision-agents app run     # single-call console
   uv run vision-agents app serve   # HTTP server
   ```

   Tip: `uv tool install vision-agents` puts the CLI on `PATH` globally, so you can drop the `uv run ` prefix.
